org.pikater.web.vaadin.gui.server.layouts.flowlayout

Interface IFlowLayoutStyleProvider


  • public interface IFlowLayoutStyleProvider
    This interface represents a dynamic style mapping to various components within a single container. Avoids having to define a lot of style names and individual style sheets.
